column2: Get two bowls, an egg, and a spoon.
Crack egg carefully with spoon.
Make a small hole on the top of the egg.
Shake egg white out of shell into the bowl.
Crack open the rest of the egg and put the yolk in a separate bowl while the rest of the white in the bowl with the egg whites.
Discard the egg shell.
